I.	Project\
\
I designed and put together a simple, automated house plant watering system. I am using the system to show how an 
\f1\i accessibility-first
\f0\i0  approach can be implemented. The end result should be simple features that serve the original goal of making the watering system engaging for as many people as possible.\
\
\
II.	What does 
\f1\i accessibility-first
\f0\i0  mean?\
\
As the name suggests, AF means that accessibility is part of the design process from the beginning. In contrast, other approaches treat accessibility features as a retrofit.\
\
