\ls2\ilvl0\cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}What is considered a disability can vary in terms of legal verbiage and societal acknowledgment.\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Disabilities can be transient. For example, a sports injury, a side-effect of a treatment, or during or after pregnancy.\
